---
---

<section class="min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center border-b-1 border-gray-200">
	<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-10 gap-2 py-10">
		<div class="col-span-full px-4 md:px-0 md:col-span-8 md:col-start-2">
			<h3>What we offer</h3>
			<h2 class="text-h2">
				Everything your brand needs to sell, scale, and show up.
			</h2>
			<p class="mt-4 text-gray-500 max-w-2xl">
				From your storefront to your social feed — we build the
				digital foundation that growing brands compete on.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-10 gap-8 pb-20">
		<!-- Card 1: Storefronts & Landing Pages -->
		<div
			class="grid col-span-1 md:col-start-2 md:col-span-2 gap-4 reveal px-4 md:px-0"
			style="animation-delay: 0.5s"
		>
			<div>
				<span class="text-2xl">🛍️</span>
				<h4 class="pt-4 text-2xl">Storefronts & Landing Pages</h4>
				<p class="text-gray-500 mt-1 text-sm">
					Your first impression, optimized to convert
				</p>
			</div>
			<p>
				Whether it's a product launch, a campaign page, or your main
				storefront — we design and build pages that turn visitors
				into buyers. Shopify, WordPress, headless — whatever fits
				your brand best.
			</p>
		</div>
		<!-- Card 2: Brand & Company Websites -->
		<div
			class="grid col-span-1 md:col-span-2 gap-4 reveal px-4 md:px-0"
			style="animation-delay: 0.62s"
		>
			<div>
				<span class="text-2xl">🏢</span>
				<h4 class="pt-4 text-2xl">Brand & Company Websites</h4>
				<p class="text-gray-500 mt-1 text-sm">
					Look the part before the meeting even starts
				</p>
			</div>
			<p>
				A strong company profile builds trust before a client,
				investor, or partner ever speaks to you. We build brand
				websites that communicate credibility, personality, and
				purpose — without looking like everyone else.
			</p>
		</div>
		<!-- Card 3: Mobile Apps -->
		<div
			class="grid col-span-1 md:col-span-2 gap-4 reveal px-4 md:px-0"
			style="animation-delay: 0.74s"
		>
			<div>
				<span class="text-2xl">📱</span>
				<h4 class="pt-4 text-2xl">Mobile Apps</h4>
				<p class="text-gray-500 mt-1 text-sm">
					Your brand, in your customer's pocket
				</p>
			</div>
			<p>
				From mobile commerce to custom brand apps — we design and
				develop mobile experiences that extend your reach beyond the
				browser. Built for real users, not just app store
				screenshots.
			</p>
		</div>
		<!-- Card 4: Social Media Management -->
		<div
			class="grid col-span-1 md:col-span-2 gap-4 reveal px-4 md:px-0"
			style="animation-delay: 0.86s"
		>
			<div>
				<span class="text-2xl">📣</span>
				<h4 class="pt-4 text-2xl">Social Media Management</h4>
				<p class="text-gray-500 mt-1 text-sm">
					Consistent presence, without the chaos
				</p>
			</div>
			<p>
				We manage your content calendar, creative direction, and
				posting — so your brand shows up consistently where your
				customers already are. Strategy-led, brand-aligned,
				growth-focused.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
